data.description: No HOA! This full brick 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home is on almost an acre of property and has been exceptionally well maintained. The Roof is 2 years old, New LVP in Owners suite, Kitchen, and both bathrooms. It is conveniently located to shopping, restaurants, and within 30 minutes of Redstone Arsenal. Don't miss your opportunity!
